- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the assembly of micro-scale objects, which is a common problem in robotics. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is also likely as the paper discusses the complexity of decision and optimization problems related to the assembly process. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper presents algorithmic results for the assembly process. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is relevant as the assembly process involves geometric constraints. 
- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the paper deals with the construction of discrete objects from particles.
